// =============================================================================
// PRAGMA defer_foreign_keys — when ON, all FK constraints behave as DEFERRED
// (i.e. checked at COMMIT instead of after each row). Auto-resets to OFF at
// the end of every transaction. No effect when foreign_keys=OFF.
// Spec §11.6 / §15.4.
// =============================================================================

